00:22:22.330 --> 00:22:23.780
I'm Murasame Reine.

00:22:24.430 --> 00:22:26.500
I teach Physics.

00:22:26.500 --> 00:22:27.670
Nice to met

00:22:33.280 --> 00:22:35.040
Physics preparation room

00:22:33.740 --> 00:22:37.250
Why are you suddenly a teacher here?

00:22:37.250 --> 00:22:40.880
What's going on, analysis officer Murasame?

00:22:40.880 --> 00:22:43.770
Just call me Reine, Shintarou.

00:22:43.770 --> 00:22:46.130
No, my name is Shido.

00:22:46.130 --> 00:22:49.680
I see. My bad, Shin.

00:22:49.680 --> 00:22:51.440
Are you even <i>trying</i> to get it right?!

00:22:51.440 --> 00:22:53.570
But that's not the point here.

00:22:53.570 --> 00:22:57.680
I'll be able to reach you quickly in case anything happens.

00:22:57.680 --> 00:23:00.440
You could've figured that out if you used your head a little,

00:23:00.440 --> 00:23:02.190
you lowly stinkbug.

00:23:02.190 --> 00:23:04.960
Never mind that. What are <i>you</i> doing here?

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:06.130
What happened to going to school?

00:23:06.130 --> 00:23:08.410
I made the proper arrangements.

00:23:11.730 --> 00:23:16.050
So... will you finally explain what you're planning to make me do?

00:23:16.050 --> 00:23:19.450
Once you've used this training software, you'll soon understand.

00:23:19.450 --> 00:23:20.540
Reine.

00:23:31.460 --> 00:23:33.260
A-A dating sim?

00:23:33.260 --> 00:23:34.970
This looks just like the one Tonomachi played.

00:23:34.970 --> 00:23:36.490
It isn't the same!

00:23:36.490 --> 00:23:37.470
Take a closer look.

00:23:40.490 --> 00:23:43.980
"My Little Shido?"

00:23:47.320 --> 00:23:49.540
Special Disaster-causing Organisms

