Good morning, Onii-tan!

00:24:24.050 --> 00:24:24.840
It's me, Ririko!

00:24:24.840 --> 00:24:26.810
Looks like things are going downhill.

00:24:26.810 --> 00:24:28.460
But I know that you'll sort it all out!

00:24:28.460 --> 00:24:30.140
I'm sure you can do it!

00:24:30.140 --> 00:24:30.910
Hey, Shido,

00:24:30.910 --> 00:24:33.740
you wouldn't want to hurt or kill the Spirits, would you?

00:24:33.740 --> 00:24:37.870
But if you let them be, they'll cause more spacequakes.

