00:24:46.020 --> 00:24:48.000
Which means, Itsuka-kun...

00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:49.360
Which means...

00:24:49.360 --> 00:24:50.340
Which means...

00:24:51.550 --> 00:24:52.760
You have to

00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:54.300
date her, date her!

00:24:54.300 --> 00:24:56.730
Make the Spirits fall for you!

00:24:56.730 --> 00:24:58.980
With friendly chatting...

00:24:58.980 --> 00:25:00.850
...lovey-dovey dates...

00:25:00.850 --> 00:25:02.770
...and your utmost charm!

00:25:02.770 --> 00:25:05.100
That's Shido-kun's...

00:25:05.100 --> 00:25:06.940
Itsuka-kun's...

00:25:06.940 --> 00:25:09.280
Onii-tan's...

00:25:09.280 --> 00:25:12.690
